      "title": "A new alliance will emerge under the leadership of Vimal",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The inauguration ceremony of the Upper Sri Lanka Alliance formed by the partner parties that left the government took place today (04) in Maharagama.",
        "Led by Member of Parliament and leader of the National Freedom Front, Vimal Weerawansa, the alliance includes Bividuru Hela Urumaya, Democratic Left Front, and the Lanka Sama Samaj Party."
      ],
